snippet.title: Dollhouse: Behind The Broken Mirror - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Enter the broken mind of Eliza de Moor, a once-celebrated singer, now trapped in the labyrinth of her own forgotten memories. With the help of a new medicine, will you be able to piece together the mystery of your past? #horrorgaming #dollhouse #indiegame

About SOEDESCO:
SOEDESCO is an independent video game developer, publisher, and distributor founded in 2002 by Soedesh Chauthi with its headquarters in Rotterdam, the Netherlands, and offices in Madrid, Spain & Pilsen, Czech Republic. We deliver creative content across multiple genres and platforms for a worldwide audience in physical and digital formats.
